data.description: N Nice rancher on over 1/2 acre lot. Updated kitchen, living room, dining room and 3/4 bath and every room is all on the main level. 2 master bedrooms with walk-in closets and bathrooms. Over-sized laundry room. Kitchen has a large walk-in pantry with sink inside. Over-sized shed in backyard. Plenty of room to build another shed or even a 3 or 4 or larger car garage. Wood floor will need to be completed in entry and hallway w/base trim and carpet in bedrooms. Home is in the middle of desirable neighborhood with land and will move fast!
